<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2611"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2611-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2611">Make all illegal acts unclassified&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3957-4049">lbaskett</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">We propose a law that automatically makes unclassified any evidence of illegal government action or policy.<br/><br/>Any person who publicly reveals classified information, information that the person can show evidences illegal government action/policy, shall be exempt from prosecution under laws pertaining to classified information.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2611" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2611', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2237&topicID=2611')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2611"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2237">Making Government Operations More Open</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=classification">classification</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=legality">legality</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=spying">spying</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=fourth amendment">fourth amendment</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=torture">torture</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2611"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2608">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2608">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2608', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2237&topicID=2608&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 64</div><div>Votes Against : 10</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2608'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2608" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 64</div><div>Votes Against : 10</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2608'))">54</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2608', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2237&topicID=2608&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
